data.name: pbUpdateTimeInformation.ToolTip
data.value:
OFF: Don't change the popup time (Default) ON: Update the popup time based on the time when you dismiss the reminder
For example: Daily Reminder with time: 10-10-2019 12:00:00. You dismiss the reminder at 12:53:00. The next popup date will be: 11-10-2019 12:53:00 instead of 12:00:00
